data.description: This newly enhanced house in a great neighborhood features 3 beds 3 baths, 2 car garage, spacious unfinished basement, freshly painted interior walls, a new installed carpet in the upper level and a waterproof CVT/Coretech vinyl laminate on main level. A freshly painted kitchen cabinets brightens its large kitchen with breakfast countertop, upgraded light fixtures, plenty of storage space and cabinets.The separate dining area that has a walkout to a concrete patio and huge backyard. The spacious living room living room with a gas fireplace and convenient TV nook.  Upstairs are the two bedrooms and a master bedroom adjourns to a master bathroom with a two sinks, a tub with shower, a separate toilet, and a large walk-in closet. You can build your family room or entertainment room, plus a guest room in the unfinished basement, or just keep it as is and use it as a storage. This popular subdivision is just 5 minutes drive  from the regional airport and about 10 minutes drive to Ft Carson and Peterson AFB, a quick and easy access to I-25, and near schools, shops, Powers First and Main shopping and entertainment center. Located between Powers and Academy Blvd.
